(23, 'com_content.article.2', '', '2023-05-23 18:37:36', 153, 3795, '2f923ce144a8731ebabea8f8ffc4a9072df9c66e', '{\"id\":2,\"asset_id\":105,\"title\":\"Lord Of The Rings: Heroes Of Middle-Earth indirmeye sunuldu\",\"alias\":\"lord-of-the-rings-heroes-of-middle-earth-indirmeye-sunuldu\",\"introtext\":\"<p>The Hobbit de dahil olmak \\u00fczere Tolkien evrenini geni\\u015f bir \\u015fekilde ele alan s\\u0131ra tabanl\\u0131 strateji t\\u00fcr\\u00fcndeki Lord Of The Rings: Heroes Of Middle-Earth mobil oyunu indirmeye sunuldu.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p>Lord Of The Rings: Gollum oyununun masa\\u00fcst\\u00fcnde \\u00f6n sipari\\u015fe a\\u00e7\\u0131lmas\\u0131n\\u0131n hemen ard\\u0131ndan Capital Games ve EA Mobile taraf\\u0131ndan geli\\u015ftirilen Lord Of The Rings: Heroes Of Middle-Earth mobil oyunu da indirmeye sunuldu.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3>Lord Of The Rings: Heroes Of Middle-Earth neler sunuyor?<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Lord Of The Rings: Heroes Of Middle-Earth s\\u0131ra tabanl\\u0131 bir RPG strateji oyunu. Oyunda farkl\\u0131 s\\u0131n\\u0131flardan farkl\\u0131 karakterlerle tak\\u0131m\\u0131n\\u0131z\\u0131 olu\\u015fturarak m\\u00fccadeleye ba\\u015fl\\u0131yorsunuz. The Hobbit de dahil olmak \\u00fczere Tolkien evrenini geni\\u015f bir \\u015fekilde ele alan oyun hem tek oyunculu hem de \\u00e7ok oyunculu PvP modlar\\u0131 bar\\u0131nd\\u0131r\\u0131yor. Oyun i\\u00e7erisinde opsiyonel sat\\u0131n al\\u0131mlar da yer al\\u0131yor ancak hi\\u00e7 para harcamadan t\\u00fcm tecr\\u00fcbeyi ya\\u015fayabiliyorsunuz.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/Resim\\/maxresdefault%201.jpg\\\" width=\\\"649\\\" height=\\\"365\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" data-path=\\\"local-images:\\/Resim\\/maxresdefault 1.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Oyuna Aragorn ve Frodo\\u2019nun ekibiyle birlikte Rivendell\\u2019e ula\\u015fmas\\u0131yla ba\\u015fl\\u0131yorsunuz. E\\u011fitim sekans\\u0131nda Nazgul ile kar\\u015f\\u0131la\\u015ft\\u0131ktan sonra as\\u0131l oynayaca\\u011f\\u013