(28, 'com_content.article.4', '', '2023-05-23 18:49:44', 153, 4619, 'f483b6bd2f52f71cbd150eead5b787345e7b4bac', '{\"id\":4,\"asset_id\":107,\"title\":\"Apex Legends Mobile oynayanlara k\\u00f6t\\u00fc haber: Oyunun fi\\u015fi \\u00e7ekiliyor\",\"alias\":\"apex-legends-mobile-oynayanlara-koetue-haber-oyunun-fisi-cekiliyor\",\"introtext\":\"<section id=\\\"160048-intro\\\" class=\\\"surmanset\\\">2022 y\\u0131l\\u0131n\\u0131n May\\u0131s ay\\u0131nda piyasaya \\u00e7\\u0131kan ve \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131yla g\\u00fc\\u00e7l\\u00fc bir ivme yakalayan Apex Legends Mobile i\\u00e7in art\\u0131k yolun sonuna gelindi. EA ve Respawn, oyunun yak\\u0131nda kapat\\u0131laca\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 duyurdu.\",\"fulltext\":\"Apex Legends geli\\u015ftiricisi Respawn Entertainment, oyunun mobil s\\u00fcr\\u00fcm\\u00fcn\\u00fcn birinci y\\u0131l d\\u00f6n\\u00fcm\\u00fcne sadece birka\\u00e7 hafta kala, 1 May\\u0131s\'ta t\\u00fcm b\\u00f6lgelerde kapat\\u0131laca\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 duyurdu. Yap\\u0131lan a\\u00e7\\u0131klamada oyun i\\u00e7i sat\\u0131n al\\u0131mlarda da herhangi bir geri \\u00f6deme yap\\u0131lmayaca\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131n alt\\u0131 \\u00e7izildi.<\\/section>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/Resim\\/Apex-Legends-Mobile-2.jpg\\\" width=\\\"695\\\" height=\\\"391\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" data-path=\\\"local-images:\\/Resim\\/Apex-Legends-Mobile-2.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<aside class=\\\"temel-bilgi\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"oge tooltip\\\" data-title=\\\"Eklenme Zaman\\u0131: 1.2.2023 13:00:00\\\">\\r\\n<h2 id=\\\"apex-legends-mobile-a-elveda\\\">Apex Legends Mobile\'a elveda<\\/h2>\\r\\n<strong>Apex Legends Mobile<\\/strong>, Respawn Entertainment ve PUBG Mobile\\u2019dan bildi\\u011fimiz Lightspeed &amp; Quantum Studios taraf\\u0131ndan geli\\u015ftirilmi\\u015fti. Oyun ilk \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131n\\u0131 son derece g\\u00fc\\u00e7l\\u00fc bir \\u015fekilde yapm\\u0131\\u015ft\\u0131 ancak Respawn, ilerleyen aylarda o Apex Legends Mobile\\u2019in\\u00a0<strong>beklenen kalite standard\\u0131n\\u0131n gerisine d\\u00fc\\u015ft\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fcn\\u00fc\\u00a0<\\/strong>s\\u00f6yl\\u00fcyor. \\u00d6te yandan halihaz\\u0131rda oyun i\\u00e7i sat\\u0131n al\\u0131mlar kapat\\u0131lm\\u0131\\u015f durumda ve oyun uygulama ma\\u011fazalar\\u0131ndan da \\u00e7ekilecek. Apex Legends Mobile\\u2019in fi\\u015finin \\u00e7ekilece\\u011fi tarih ise<strong>\\u00a01 May\\u0131s.<\\/strong><br \\/>\\r\\n<p>Bununla birlikte, gelecekte mobil cihazlarda yeni bir t\\u00fcr Apex olabilir gibi g\\u00f6r\\u00fcn\\u00fcyor. EA CEO\\u2019su Andrew Wilson, EA ve geli\\u015ftirme orta\\u011f\\u0131 Respawn\\u2019\\u0131n oyunun bu \\\"versiyonunu\\\" sonland\\u0131rmay\\u0131 se\\u00e7tiklerini ve \\u015firketin \\\"gelecekte ba\\u011flant\\u0131l\\u0131 bir Apex mobil deneyimini yeniden tasarlamay\\u0131 planlad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131\\\" s\\u00f6yledi. Bu arada EA, Nisan 2021\'de duyurmay\\u0131 planlad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131\\u00a0<strong>Battlefield mobil oyununun geli\\u015ftirilmesini de durduruyor.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/aside>\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":10,\"created\":\"2023-05-23 18:49:44\",\"created_by\":153,\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-05-23 18:49:44\",\"modified_by\":153,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2023-05-23 18:49:44\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/Resim\\\\\\/Apex-Legends-Mobile.jpg#joomlaImage:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/local-images\\\\\\/Resim\\\\\\/Apex-Legends-Mobile.jpg?width=1023&height=575\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\