Legends Mobile\\u2019in\\u00a0<strong>beklenen kalite standard\\u0131n\\u0131n gerisine d\\u00fc\\u015ft\\u00fc\\u011f\\u00fcn\\u00fc\\u00a0<\\/strong>s\\u00f6yl\\u00fcyor. \\u00d6te yandan halihaz\\u0131rda oyun i\\u00e7i sat\\u0131n al\\u0131mlar kapat\\u0131lm\\u0131\\u015f durumda ve oyun uygulama ma\\u011fazalar\\u0131ndan da \\u00e7ekilecek. Apex Legends Mobile\\u2019in fi\\u015finin \\u00e7ekilece\\u011fi tarih ise<strong>\\u00a01 May\\u0131s.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br \\/>Bununla birlikte, gelecekte mobil cihazlarda yeni bir t\\u00fcr Apex olabilir gibi g\\u00f6r\\u00fcn\\u00fcyor. EA CEO\\u2019su Andrew Wilson, EA ve geli\\u015ftirme orta\\u011f\\u0131 Respawn\\u2019\\u0131n oyunun bu \\\"versiyonunu\\\" sonland\\u0131rmay\\u0131 se\\u00e7tiklerini ve \\u015firketin \\\"gelecekte ba\\u011flant\\u0131l\\u0131 bir Apex mobil deneyimini yeniden tasarlamay\\u0131 planlad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131\\\" s\\u00f6yledi. Bu arada EA, Nisan 2021\'de duyurmay\\u0131 planlad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131\\u00a0<strong>Battlefield mobil oyununun geli\\u015ftirilmesini de durduruyor.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/aside>\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":10,\"created\":\"2023-05-23 18:49:44\",\"created_by\":\"153\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-05-23 18:51:19\",\"modified_by\":153,\"checked_out\":153,\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-05-23 18:51:10\",\"publish_up\":\"2023-05-23 18:49:44\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/Resim\\\\\\/Apex-Legends-Mobile.jpg#joomlaImage:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/local-images\\\\\\/Resim\\\\\\/Apex-Legends-Mobile.jpg?width=1023&height=575\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"tar