(34, 'com_content.article.5', '', '2023-05-23 18:54:08', 153, 4997, '9d9b0116ecf627b191a6998f69154cf16755de30', '{\"id\":5,\"asset_id\":108,\"title\":\"Yeni Dead by Daylight oyunu duyuruldu\",\"alias\":\"yeni-dead-by-daylight-oyunu-duyuruldu\",\"introtext\":\"<section id=\\\"163947-intro\\\" class=\\\"surmanset\\\">Supermassive Games\'in pop\\u00fcler oyunu Dead by Daylight\'\\u0131n yenisi geliyor. Until Dawn geli\\u015ftiricisi taraf\\u0131ndan duyurulan yeni Dead by Daylight oyununun nas\\u0131l olaca\\u011f\\u0131na dair detaylar sizlerle.\",\"fulltext\":\"<strong>Dead by Daylight<\\/strong>\\u00a0hala pop\\u00fclerli\\u011fini s\\u00fcrd\\u00fcren ve en ba\\u015far\\u0131l\\u0131 asimetrik korku oyunlar\\u0131ndan biri. 10 y\\u0131l\\u0131 a\\u015fk\\u0131n bir s\\u00fcre \\u00f6nce yay\\u0131nland\\u0131 ve \\u00f6zellikle de ekip serinin gelece\\u011fine dair planlar\\u0131n\\u0131 a\\u00e7\\u0131klad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 i\\u00e7in hala ilgi ile oynan\\u0131yor. Ayr\\u0131ca oyuncu kitlesi g\\u00fcn ge\\u00e7tik\\u00e7e art\\u0131yor.<\\/section>\\r\\n<section class=\\\"surmanset\\\">\\r\\n<h2 id=\\\"yeni-karakterler-olacak-ve-sisin-otesinde-gececek\\\">Yeni karakterler olacak ve sisin \\u00f6tesinde ge\\u00e7ecek<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/Resim\\/yeni-dead-by-daylight-oyunu-geliyor163947_0.jpg\\\" width=\\\"795\\\" height=\\\"415\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" data-path=\\\"local-images:\\/Resim\\/yeni-dead-by-daylight-oyunu-geliyor163947_0.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p id=\\\"163947-paragraph-0\\\"><strong>Until Dawn<\\/strong>\\u00a0ve\\u00a0<strong>The Quarry<\\/strong>\\u00a0gibi son derece ba\\u015far\\u0131l\\u0131 tek oyunculu korku oyunlar\\u0131n\\u0131n arkas\\u0131ndaki ekip\\u00a0<strong>Supermassive Games<\\/strong>, yeni bir Dead by Daylight oyunu \\u00fczerinde \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131yor. Supermassive\'in di\\u011fer oyunlar\\u0131nda oldu\\u011fu gibi bu oyun da tek oyunculu bir oyun olacak. Yap\\u0131lan bas\\u0131n a\\u00e7\\u0131