(42, 'com_content.article.8', '', '2023-05-23 19:07:34', 153, 4056, '83ae6702231caad954b80910574cbcf90b70606f', '{\"id\":8,\"asset_id\":111,\"title\":\"Call of Duty Warzone 2\\u2019nin \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015f tarihi belli oldu! \\u00d6ny\\u00fckleme a\\u00e7\\u0131ld\\u0131\",\"alias\":\"call-of-duty-warzone-2nin-cikis-tarihi-belli-oldu-oenyuekleme-acildi\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Uzun zamand\\u0131r merakla beklenen ve Modern Warfare 2 (2022) mekaniklerini kullanan Warzone 2 \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015f tarihi belli oldu. Hatta \\u00f6ny\\u00fcklemeye a\\u00e7\\u0131ld\\u0131.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p>PUBG ile pop\\u00fclerle\\u015fen Battle Royal ak\\u0131m\\u0131na uyan oyunlar aras\\u0131nda CoD serisi de yer al\\u0131yor. Yenilenen Call of Duty: Modern Warfare (2019) ile birlikte \\u00e7\\u0131kan Warzone, b\\u00fcy\\u00fck ilgi \\u00e7ekti. Devam oyunu ise merakla bekleniyordu. Modern Warfare 2 (2022)\\u2019nin mekaniklerini kullanarak oyunculara FPS Battle Royal deneyimi sunan Warzone 2 \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015f tarihi belli oldu. Hatta \\u00f6ny\\u00fcklemeye a\\u00e7\\u0131ld\\u0131.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2 id=\\\"h-warzone-2-cikis-tarihi-simdiden-yukleyebilirsiniz\\\" class=\\\"has-vivid-red-color has-text-color\\\">Warzone 2 \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015f tarihi! \\u015eimdiden y\\u00fckleyebilirsiniz<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2\\u2019nin \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131 \\u00fczerinden 1 ay ge\\u00e7ti. Oyuncular taraf\\u0131ndan be\\u011fenilen yap\\u0131m, hikayeden daha \\u00e7ok online modu ile \\u00f6n plana \\u00e7\\u0131k\\u0131yor. Fiyat\\u0131 ile tart\\u0131\\u015fma konusu olsa da Activision, online modu i\\u00e7in almak isteyenlere Warzone 2\\u2019yi sunuyor. T\\u00fcrkiye saatlerine g\\u00f6re 16 Kas\\u0131m 2022 \\u00c7ar\\u015famba, yani bug\\u00fcn oynan\\u0131\\u015fa sunuluyor. Fakat erkenden \\u00f6ny\\u00fckleme yapabilirsiniz.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/Resim\\/warzone-2.jpg\\\" width=\\\"759\\\" height=\\\"427\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" data-path=\\\"local-images:\\/Resim\\/warzone-2.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Warzone 2 PC, PlayStation 4 ve PlayStation 5 , Xbox One ve Xbox Series X\\/S i\\u00e7in \\u00f6ny\\u00fcklenebilir durumda. Oyunu bilgisayar i\\u00e7in Activision\\u2019un kendi uygulamas\\u0131 Battle.net veya Steam\\u00a0\\u00fczerinden, XBOX ve PlayStation i\\u00e7in de XBOX Games Store ve PlayStation Store \\u00fczerinden indirebilirsiniz.<\\/p>\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":12,\"created\":\"2023-05-23 19:07:34\",\"created_by\":153,\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-05-23 19:07:34\",\"modified_by\":153,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2023-05-23 19:07:34\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/Resim\\\\\\/Meta_S2_WZ2_1920x1080.jpg#joomlaImage:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/local-images\\\\\\/Resim\\\\\\/Meta_S2_WZ2_1920x1080.jpg?width=1920&height=1080\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"sh