(111, 'com_content.article.1', '', '2023-05-24 00:35:37', 153, 4650, 'e850d9a71221ac9a8fb717b30f12fbbbf21bf727', '{\"id\":\"1\",\"asset_id\":104,\"title\":\"S\\u0131z\\u0131nt\\u0131lardan yola \\u00e7\\u0131karak haz\\u0131rlanan GTA 6 fragman\\u0131 izleyenleri b\\u00fcy\\u00fcledi\",\"alias\":\"sizintilardan-yola-cikarak-hazirlanan-gta-6-fragmani-izleyenleri-bueyueledi\",\"introtext\":\"<section id=\\\"164002-intro\\\" class=\\\"surmanset\\\">Grand Theft Auto hayranlar\\u0131ndan biri Eyl\\u00fcl ay\\u0131ndaki b\\u00fcy\\u00fck s\\u0131z\\u0131nt\\u0131ya dayanan iki dakikal\\u0131k bir GTA 6 fragman\\u0131 haz\\u0131rlad\\u0131. Tam 200 g\\u00fcnde olu\\u015fturulan g\\u00f6r\\u00fcnt\\u00fcler izleyenlerde hayranl\\u0131k uyand\\u0131r\\u0131yor.\",\"fulltext\":\"<br \\/><br \\/>\\r\\n<p>Grand Theft Auto\'nun alt\\u0131nc\\u0131 b\\u00f6l\\u00fcm\\u00fc oyun severler taraf\\u0131ndan b\\u00fcy\\u00fck bir heyecanla bekleniyor. Rockstar Games oyunun geli\\u015fini \\u00e7oktan onaylam\\u0131\\u015f olsa da hen\\u00fcz GTA 6 ile ilgili merak giderecek \\u00e7ok fazla resmi bilgi yok. Serinin hayranlar\\u0131ndan biri bu bekleyi\\u015fi bir nebze de olsa giderecek bir i\\u015fe imza att\\u0131.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>12th Hour isimli YouTube kanal\\u0131n\\u0131n sahibi oyun hakk\\u0131ndaki s\\u0131z\\u0131nt\\u0131 ve s\\u00f6ylentilere dayanarak kendi GTA 6 fragman\\u0131n\\u0131 haz\\u0131rlad\\u0131. Fortnite montajlar\\u0131yla \\u00fcnlenen kanal bu fan yap\\u0131m\\u0131 fragman\\u0131 Unreal Engine 5, Blender ve kendi paras\\u0131yla sat\\u0131n ald\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 materyalleri kullanarak olu\\u015fturdu\\u011funu s\\u00f6yl\\u00fcyor.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/section>\\r\\n<section class=\\\"surmanset\\\"><\\/section>\\r\\n<section class=\\\"surmanset\\\"><\\/section>\\r\\n<section class=\\\"surmanset\\\"><\\/section>\\r\\n<section class=\\\"surmanset\\\"><\\/section>\\r\\n<section class=\\\"surmanset\\\"><\\/section>\\r\\n<section class=\\\"surmanset\\\"><\\/section